{"tid":2141122,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交轉機 台與索馬利蘭互設代表處","createTime":"2020-08-05T12:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T12:27:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fedfc812d6eceec00c78117674d13f1a4f7332d1","tid":2141122,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:27:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200805/YIGP2435KUNV3F4BMFFQWUBVUM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200805%2FYIGP2435KUNV3F4BMFFQWUBVUM%2F&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F51DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=7f9eb6c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200805%2FYIGP2435KUNV3F4BMFFQWUBVUM%2F&h=e8e1a592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200805/YIGP2435KUNV3F4BMFFQWUBVUM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n外交轉機 台與索馬利蘭互設代表處<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Z2xa2-sMRSDuD4EzTmEBG00ZgTU=/190x106/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZGMMMBDAXZUHABXDGRY7XBXAAE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZ2xa2-sMRSDuD4EzTmEBG00ZgTU%3D%2F190x106%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZGMMMBDAXZUHABXDGRY7XBXAAE.gif&h=0693f909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際空間長期被大陸打壓的台灣，外交工作最近出現新轉機。台灣與位於東非的索馬利蘭（Republic of Somaliland，圖）將互設具官方性質的代表處，台外交部證實，計劃在8、9月完成設處工作。北京派遣的代表團今日抵達索國，相信是為外交事務進行遊說。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北京代表赴索攪局<br />\n<br />\n與台灣同樣未被國際承認為國家的索馬利蘭，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《索馬利蘭紀事報》報道，索馬利蘭總統。。。。。。。。。。。組織的正式承認。<br />\n<br />\n另外，台北當局預計本月底至下月初會重開駐關島辦事處，現正與美方協調中，但仍然要考慮疫情發展。若成事，將令台灣在美代表處數目，增至13個。<br />\n<br />\n中央社"}]}